dct_description_sm: Relief shown by hachures. Insets: Massaua -- Massaua und Umgegend. In upper margin: Carl Flemmings Generalkarten. No. 42. Shows site of explorations by Gerhard Rohlfs in the Sahara in 1879.
dct_publisher_sm: Glogau : Druck und Verlag von Carl Flemming, [ca. 1880]
